17,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"要set軍規，我哋唔係白衫/黑警。我哋是要對準政權，唔好傷及無辜！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要set軍規</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n光復香港🇭🇰時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不割蓆 不篤灰 不互屌</strong></span>"},{"pid":"540413f10f871b556ca96f4c082beee0b51a1e5a","tid":1466290,"uid":124030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不互屌<br />\n係要一齊檢討</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">無忘721<br />\n無忘811</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尊重在場決定<br />\n希望大家會理性討論<br />\n一齊進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692eced9543625aba7a12e02c0c6b2e1d6244694","tid":1466290,"uid":198290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fb31e62cda965420efa57874a6f251dbcf6e8831","tid":1466290,"uid":124030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"大家想一想死去嘅烈士<br />\n送頭幾百手足前途生死未卜<br />\n仲有一班響醫院⋯<br />\n<br />\n唔想大家重蹈雨傘覆轍！<br />\n<br />\n所以求求大家不互屌<br />\n而係要理性檢討！<br />\n我地會一次比一次進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不互屌<br />\n係要一齊檢討</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">無忘721<br />\n無忘811</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:45:10.000Z","msg":"我建議聽日入機場嘅人，可唔可以揾一班人去主動幫手或者解答有機場入面未飛到